OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds
OL,6,Fand pleasantly warm sunny spells to
OL,7,Fend the day. However, cloud will
OL,8,Fincrease from the west overnight, but
OL,9,Fremaining dry for all. A slightly
OL,10,Fmilder night for most under the
OL,11,Fblanket of cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FRather cloudy to start the
OL,14,Fday, the cloud then tending to break
OL,15,Fup a little allowing frequent showers
OL,16,Fto develop, some heavy with thunder
OL,17,Fpossible towards the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
